<p class="eyebrow"><a href="/integrators/">For integrators</a> / Hosted PBX</p>
<h1>Hosted PBX for one office or one hundred tenants.</h1>
<p class="lede"><a href="/pbx/">VoiceTel Hosted PBX</a> gives organizations a fully managed phone system tied directly to VoiceTel numbers, SIP routing, emergency-service configuration, and support. Built on VoiceML, designed for flexibility and carrier-grade resiliency.</p>
<p>For partners, Hosted PBX is multi-tenant from the ground up. Each tenant in a partner account has its own portal scope, caller IDs, emergency-service records, users, and CDRs. Scale from one office to many customer locations.</p>
<p class="hero-actions">
	<a class="btn btn-primary" href="/contact/">Become a partner</a>
	<a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/pbx/">Hosted PBX overview</a>
</p>

