<section class="section-block">
	<h2>Give users business calling across web, desktop, and mobile</h2>
	<p><a href="/phone/">VoiceTel Phone</a> gives users a consistent calling experience across browser, Windows, macOS, Linux, iOS, and Android. Provisioning remains tied to VoiceTel SIP credentials and account controls.</p>
	<p>A clean way to support remote workers, hybrid teams, deskless employees, mobile users, and customers who don't want to rely only on desk phones.</p>

